{"tha-ap491:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap491:0.2":"Pamsukulavagga ","tha-ap491:0.3":"9 Dhammaruciyattheraapadana ","tha-ap491:1.1":"“Yada dipankaro buddho, ","tha-ap491:1.2":"sumedham byakari jino; ","tha-ap491:1.3":"‘Aparimeyye ito kappe, ","tha-ap491:1.4":"ayam buddho bhavissati. ","tha-ap491:2.1":"Imassa janika mata, ","tha-ap491:2.2":"maya nama bhavissati; ","tha-ap491:2.3":"Pita suddhodano nama, ","tha-ap491:2.4":"ayam hessati gotamo. ","tha-ap491:3.1":"Padhanam padahitvana, ","tha-ap491:3.2":"katva dukkarakarikam; ","tha-ap491:3.3":"Assatthamule sambuddho, ","tha-ap491:3.4":"bujjhissati mahayaso. ","tha-ap491:4.1":"Upatisso kolito ca, ","tha-ap491:4.2":"agga hessanti savaka; ","tha-ap491:4.3":"Anando nama namena, ","tha-ap491:4.4":"upatthissatimam jinam. ","tha-ap491:5.1":"Khema uppalavanna ca, ","tha-ap491:5.2":"agga hessanti savika; ","tha-ap491:5.3":"Citto alavako ceva, ","tha-ap491:5.4":"agga hessantupasaka. ","tha-ap491:6.1":"Khujjuttara nandamata, ","tha-ap491:6.2":"agga hessantupasika; ","tha-ap491:6.3":"Bodhi imassa virassa, ","tha-ap491:6.4":"assatthoti pavuccati’. ","tha-ap491:7.1":"Idam sutvana vacanam, ","tha-ap491:7.2":"asamassa mahesino; ","tha-ap491:7.3":"Amodita naramaru, ","tha-ap491:7.4":"namassanti katanjali. ","tha-ap491:8.1":"Tadaham manavo asim, ","tha-ap491:8.2":"megho nama susikkhito; ","tha-ap491:8.3":"Sutva byakaranam settham, ","tha-ap491:8.4":"sumedhassa mahamune. ","tha-ap491:9.1":"Samvisattho bhavitvana, ","tha-ap491:9.2":"sumedhe karunasaye; ","tha-ap491:9.3":"Pabbajantanca tam viram, ","tha-ap491:9.4":"sahava anupabbajim. ","tha-ap491:10.1":"Samvuto patimokkhasmim, ","tha-ap491:10.2":"indriyesu ca pancasu; ","tha-ap491:10.3":"Suddhajivo sato viro, ","tha-ap491:10.4":"jinasasanakarako. ","tha-ap491:11.1":"Evam viharamanoham, ","tha-ap491:11.2":"papamittena kenaci; ","tha-ap491:11.3":"Niyojito anacare, ","tha-ap491:11.4":"sumagga paridhamsito. ","tha-ap491:12.1":"Vitakkavasiko hutva, ","tha-ap491:12.2":"sasanato apakkamim; ","tha-ap491:12.3":"Paccha tena kumittena, ","tha-ap491:12.4":"payutto matughatanam. ","tha-ap491:13.1":"Akarim anantariyam, ","tha-ap491:13.2":"ghatayim dutthamanaso; ","tha-ap491:13.3":"Tato cuto mahavicim, ","tha-ap491:13.4":"upapanno sudarunam. ","tha-ap491:14.1":"Vinipatagato santo, ","tha-ap491:14.2":"samsarim dukkhito ciram; ","tha-ap491:14.3":"Na puno addasam viram, ","tha-ap491:14.4":"sumedham narapungavam. ","tha-ap491:15.1":"Asmim kappe samuddamhi, ","tha-ap491:15.2":"maccho asim timingalo; ","tha-ap491:15.3":"Disvaham sagare navam, ","tha-ap491:15.4":"gocaratthamupagamim. ","tha-ap491:16.1":"Disva mam vanija bhita, ","tha-ap491:16.2":"buddhasetthamanussarum; ","tha-ap491:16.3":"Gotamoti mahaghosam, ","tha-ap491:16.4":"sutva tehi udiritam. ","tha-ap491:17.1":"Pubbasannam saritvana, ","tha-ap491:17.2":"tato kalankato aham; ","tha-ap491:17.3":"Savatthiyam kule iddhe, ","tha-ap491:17.4":"jato brahmanajatiyam. ","tha-ap491:18.1":"Asim dhammaruci nama, ","tha-ap491:18.2":"sabbapapajigucchako; ","tha-ap491:18.3":"Disvaham lokapajjotam, ","tha-ap491:18.4":"jatiya sattavassiko. ","tha-ap491:19.1":"Mahajetavanam gantva, ","tha-ap491:19.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","tha-ap491:19.3":"Upemi buddham tikkhattum, ","tha-ap491:19.4":"rattiya divasassa ca. ","tha-ap491:20.1":"Tada disva muni aha, ","tha-ap491:20.2":"ciram dhammaruciti mam; ","tha-ap491:20.3":"Tatoham avacam buddham, ","tha-ap491:20.4":"pubbakammapabhavitam. ","tha-ap491:21.1":"Suciram satapunnalakkhanam, ","tha-ap491:21.2":"Patipubbena visuddhapaccayam; ","tha-ap491:21.3":"Ahamajjasupekkhanam vata, ","tha-ap491:21.4":"Tava passami nirupamam viggaham. ","tha-ap491:22.1":"Suciram vihatattamo maya, ","tha-ap491:22.2":"Sucirakkhena nadi visosita; ","tha-ap491:22.3":"Suciram amalam visodhitam, ","tha-ap491:22.4":"Nayanam nanamayam mahamune. ","tha-ap491:23.1":"Cirakalasamangito taya, ","tha-ap491:23.2":"Avinattho punarantaram ciram; ","tha-ap491:23.3":"Punarajjasamagato taya, ","tha-ap491:23.4":"Na hi nassanti katani gotama. ","tha-ap491:24.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap491:24.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap491:24.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap491:25.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap491:25.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap491:25.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap491:26.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap491:26.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap491:26.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap491:27.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma dhammaruciyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap491:28.1":"Dhammaruciyattherassapadanam navamam. "}